{"tid":320302,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫生請入]近排身體有d唔妥","createTime":"2017-07-13T12:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T12:42:05.000Z","uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c845da0f68231263a168341f12dd96e4a60caa1","tid":320302,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"我廿六，幾個月感覺都身體有d唔妥，唔知咩事<br />\n1.瘦左，但我平時食好多野，一日四餐，晚餐至少兩碗飯<br />\n2.手震，唔係柏金遜嗰種，一般生活唔會有人留意到，細心d望一陣就會陣<br />\n3.腳震，企十幾秒就開始震，似做完運動好攰嗰種<br />\n4.崩牙，唔知關唔關事，平時咬手指甲，但今日冇啦啦門牙崩左少少，大約係四分一粒米<br />\n<br />\n會睇醫生，但唔知邊個好<br />\n驚佢就咁比抗生素我就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557f64837aaf9febbd0c02fdf84df94fc90b9b5d","tid":320302,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"壓力大，焦慮症<br />\n<br />\n利申9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2912586e30d1fd15d4ab33047c5a2c0e36906792","tid":320302,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"甲亢？"},{"pid":"f2631a596ed82373bdb3219194c68fcdcb216c55","tid":320302,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"睇第一項以為係cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c24180332ed416bfcfe78fb83f11607329a70f","tid":320302,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壓力大，焦慮症<br />\n<br />\n利申9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔係，我食好住好番工好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026607731e88dd006a3d00b591c43da585ff7d7f","tid":320302,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甲亢？</blockquote><br />\n睇左有d似，有冇醫生推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318327aa7299